<li class='cover' id='bookCover_39798828'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/39798828-the-fall-of-gondolin"><img alt="The Fall of Gondolin (Middle-Earth Universe)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1535688410l/39798828._SY75_.jpg" />
